<section xml:id="sec-stradella-bass-keyboard-layout" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Stradella Bass Keyboard Layout</title>
  <p>This section will cover the layout of the Stradella bass keyboard and its use in chord and scale construction.</p>

